Minmetals Land 6-Month Contracted Sales Rise to 2.5 Billion Yuan

-- B y   C a t h y   C h a n
-- 
2011-07-07T13:55:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-07/minmetals-land-6-month-contracted-sales-rise-to-2-5-billion-yuan.html
Minmetals Land Ltd. (230)  said first-half
contracted sales increased 263 percent from a year earlier to
2.5 billion yuan ($387 million), even as the average selling
price fell 8 percent to 9,000 yuan a square meter.  Contracted gross floor area sales almost quadrupled to
about 276,000 square meters (3 million square feet), the company
said in an e-mailed press release today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Cathy Chan in Hong Kong at 
 kchan14@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nerys Avery at 
 Navery2@bloomberg.net  